# Single-module LoD addon. Loads exactly one Data file: the bundled
# BattlePetAbilities catalog for the Mainline / Retail flavor. The core library will
# auto-LoadAddOn this addon on the first :Get miss against BattlePetAbilities.

Data\BattlePetAbilities.lua
